#: ../../content/soins/registres.md:1
msgid "Clinical Registers"
msgstr "Klinische registers"

#: ../../content/soins/registres.md:4
msgid ""
"Resthome's clinical registers — falls, pressure ulcers (Braden), wounds, "
"pain, restraint, nutrition (MNA), continence, mobility, cognition."
msgstr ""
"De klinische registers van Resthome — vallen, doorligwonden (Braden), "
"wonden, pijn, fixatie, voeding (MNA), continentie, mobiliteit, cognitie."

#: ../../content/soins/registres.md:7
msgid ""
"**Clinical registers** structure the monitoring of risks and geriatric "
"assessments. Each register groups together the assessments of a single "
"theme, over time, for each resident."
msgstr ""
"De **klinische registers** structureren de opvolging van risico's en "
"geriatrische evaluaties. Elk register bundelt de evaluaties van eenzelfde "
"thema, in de tijd, voor elke bewoner."

